\c 1
\s Inzalo kaAdamu
\p
\v 1 UAdamu, uSeti, uEnosi,
\v 2 uKenani, uMahalaleli, uJaredi,
\v 3 uEnoki, uMethusela, uLameki,
\v 4 uNowa, uShemu, uHamu, loJafethi\x + Gen. 4.25,26. 5.3,6,9,12,15,18,21,25,29,32.\x*.
\s Inzalo yamadodana kaNowa
\p
\v 5 Amadodana kaJafethi: OGomeri loMagogi\x + Gen. 10.2-5.\x* loMadayi loJavani loThubhali loMesheki loTirasi\x + 2 Kho. 17.6.\x*.
\v 6 Lamadodana kaGomeri: OAshikenazi loRifathi loTogarma\x + Gen. 10.3.\x*.
\v 7 Lamadodana kaJavani: OElisha loTarshishi, amaKiti lamaDodani\x + 1 Kho. 10.22.\x*.
\p
\v 8 Amadodana kaHamu: OKushi loMizirayimi, uPuti loKhanani.
\v 9 Lamadodana kaKushi: OSeba loHavila loSabitha loRahama loSabitheka. Lamadodana kaRahama: OShebha loDedani.
\v 10 UKushi wasezala uNimrodi; yena waqala ukuba liqhawe emhlabeni.
\v 11 UMizirayimi wasezala amaLudi lamaAnami lamaLehabi lamaNafethuhi
\v 12 lamaPatrusi lamaKaseluhi (okwaphuma kiwo amaFilisti), lamaKafitori.
\v 13 UKhanani wasezala uSidoni izibulo lakhe, loHethi,
\v 14 lomJebusi lomAmori lomGirigashi
\v 15 lomHivi lomArki lomSini
\v 16 lomArvadi lomZemari lomHamathi\x + Gen. 10.6-8.10.13-18.\x*.
\p
\v 17 Amadodana kaShemu: OElamu loAshuri loArpakishadi loLudi loAramu\x + Gen. 10.22-29. 11.10.\x* loUzi loHuli loGetheri loMesheki\x + Gen. 10.23.\x*.
\v 18 UArpakishadi wasezala uShela; uShela wasezala uEberi\x + Gen. 10.24. 11.13.\x*.
\v 19 UEberi wasezalelwa amadodana amabili. Ibizo lenye lalinguPelegi, ngoba ensukwini zayo umhlaba wadatshulwa; lebizo lomfowabo lalinguJokithani.
\v 20 UJokithani wasezala oAlimodadi loShelefi loHazamavethi loJera
\v 21 loHadoramu loUzali loDikila
\v 22 loEbhali loAbhimayeli loShebha\x + Gen. 10.28.\x*
\v 23 loOfiri loHavila loJobabi. Bonke labo babengamadodana kaJokithani.
\s Inzalo kaShemu
\p
\v 24 UShemu\x + Gen. 11.10-26. Luka 3.34-36.\x*, uArpakishadi, uShela\x + Gen. 10.24. 11.13.\x*,
\v 25 uEberi, uPelegi, uRewu,
\v 26 uSerugi, uNahori, uTera,
\v 27 uAbrama; onguAbrahama\x + Gen. 17.5.\x*.
\v 28 Amadodana kaAbrahama: OIsaka\x + Gen. 21.2,3.\x* loIshmayeli\x + Gen. 16.11,15.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaIshmayeli
\p
\v 29 Laba yizizukulwana zabo: Izibulo likaIshmayeli\x + Gen. 25.13-16.\x*, uNebayothi\x + Isa. 60.7.\x*, loKedari, loAdibeli, loMibisama,
\v 30 uMishima, loDuma, uMasa, uHadadi, loTema,
\v 31 uJeturi, uNafishi, loKedema; la ngamadodana kaIshmayeli\x + Isa. 60.7.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaAbrahama kuKetura
\p
\v 32 Njalo amadodana kaKetura, umfazi omncinyane kaAbrahama\x + Gen. 25.1-4.\x*: Wazala oZimrani loJokishani loMedani loMidiyani loIshibaki loShuwa\x + Jobe 2.11.\x*. Amadodana-ke kaJokishani: OShebha loDedani\x + 1.9.\x*.
\v 33 Lamadodana kaMidiyani\x + Isa. 60.6. Hlu. 6.1.\x*: OEfa loEferi\x + Isa. 60.6. Hlu. 6.1.\x* loHanoki loAbida loElidaha. Bonke laba ngamadodana kaKetura\x + Gen. 25.4.\x*.
\v 34 UAbrahama wasezala uIsaka\x + Gen. 21.2,3.\x*. Amadodana kaIsaka: OEsawu loIsrayeli\x + Gen. 25.25,26.\x*.
\s Inzalo kaEsawu
\p
\v 35 Amadodana kaEsawu: OElifazi, uRehuweli, loJewushi, loJalamu, loKora\x + Gen. 36.4,5,9-13.\x*.
\v 36 Amadodana kaElifazi: OThemani, loOmari, uZefi, loGatama, uKenazi, loTimina, loAmaleki\x + 1.39. Gen. 36.12.\x*.
\v 37 Amadodana kaRehuweli: ONahathi, uZera, uShama, loMiza.
\v 38 Lamadodana kaSeyiri: OLotani loShobhali loZibeyoni loAna loDishoni loEzeri loDishani.
\v 39 Lamadodana kaLotani: OHori loHomama; lodadewabo kaLotani wayenguTimina.
\v 40 Amadodana kaShobhali: OAliyani, loManahathi, loEbhali, uShefi, loOnama\x + Gen. 36.20-28.\x*. Lamadodana kaZibeyoni: OAya loAna.
\v 41 Amadodana kaAna: UDishoni. Lamadodana kaDishoni: OHamrani loEshibhani loJitirani loKerani\x + 1.38.\x*.
\v 42 Amadodana kaEzeri: OBilihani loZahavana\x + Gen. 36.27.\x*, uJahakhani\x + Nani 33.31.\x*. Amadodana kaDishani: OUzi loArani.
\p
\v 43 Njalo la ngamakhosi abusa elizweni leEdoma, kungakabusi inkosi phezu kwabantwana bakoIsrayeli: UBhela indodana kaBeyori; lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiDinihaba.
\v 44 UBhela wasesifa, uJobabi indodana kaZera weBhozira wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 45 UJobabi wasesifa, uHushama owelizweni lamaThemani wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 46 UHushama wasesifa, uHadadi indodana kaBedadi, owatshaya amaMidiyani emagcekeni akoMowabi, wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe; lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiAvithi.
\v 47 UHadadi wasesifa, uSamila weMasireka wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe.
\v 48 USamila wasesifa, uShawuli weRehobothi emfuleni wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + Gen. 36.37,38.\x*.
\v 49 UShawuli wasesifa, uBhali-Hanani indodana kaAkhibhori wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe\x + Gen. 36.37,38.\x*.
\v 50 UBhali-Hanani wasesifa, uHadadi wasesiba yinkosi esikhundleni sakhe; lebizo lomuzi wakhe laliyiPhayi; lebizo lomkakhe lalinguMehethabheli indodakazi kaMatiredi indodakazi kaMezahabhi.
\v 51 UHadadi wasesifa. Lezinduna zeEdoma zaziyi\add lezi\add*: Induna uTimina, induna uAliya, induna uJethethi,
\v 52 induna uAholibama, induna uEla, induna uPinoni,
\v 53 induna uKenazi, induna uThemani, induna uMibhizari,
\v 54 induna uMagidiyeli, induna uIrama; lezi yizinduna zeEdoma.